  "texts": [
    "3.3) was correct (Table 3).",
    "Aside from the IncFII, MOBP plasmid mentioned earlier, a second and third plasmid, contig 2 and 4 in the reference genome, were also found in all isolates.",
    "A fourth plasmid, contig 7 in the reference, was detected in all isolates, but not in the metagenomic assembly.",
    "In the reference and isolate 2 it represented a small plasmid of 6,446 bp, but in isolate 1 it was detected as a 3,223 bp plasmid.",
    "Interestingly, the plasmid contig that was binned with E. coli in the sample A metagenomic results (contig 866 on Figure 3A) did not have a counterpart in the plasmids from the reference genome."
  ]
